rownames(all.acc) <- c("Lasso", "Logit Boost", "SVM", "RF", "PLS", "xgbTree")

health_df_plasma_full <- health_df_plasma_full[, -c(2, 3)]
health_df_plasma_full.test <- health_df_plasma_full.test[, -c(2, 3)]
